target: Do you need help with anything else?
context: <user>  Please help play a song. I am really in a bad mood. <system>  What genre of songs do you prefer? <user>  I feel like listening to The Water Fountain song. <system>  Please have it check, play the song The Water Fountain on the TV. <user>  Yes, everything is right. I forgot what album it does belong, I used to listen to it when it was first released. <system>  It is from Narrated For You album. The song has started playing at the TV. <user>  Thanks! It soothes my mood. Now I need to make a transfer to a savings account. I promised that I will lend my brother a small amount money. <system>  What do you want me to use?<user>  Please use my savings account too. <system>  Who is the recipient of this transfer and how much would you like to transfer?<user>  Send it to Amy, my brother's wife. Please transfer an amount of $1440. They need to buy a new laptop. <system>  Please do confirm the following details: transfer from your savings account an amount of $1,440 to Amy in their savings account.<user>  That's right. <system>  The transfer has been successful.<user>  Thank you so much! Now I want to watch a movie. <system>  DO you have something in mind?<user>  Yes, I want to watch Josie and the Pussycats. I heard its a good movie. <system>  Please do confirm the following details: you would like to play Josie and the Pussycats without subtitles.<user>  Yes, you got it correctly. <system>  The movie has started playing.<user>  Thanks again! You're such a big help. <system>
